{"tid":844395,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視稱記者孔琳琳已獲釋　大使館說有中國記者遭阻撓","createTime":"2018-10-02T00:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T00:31:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a234a87c648f2550024e452155934ea935f77a75","tid":844395,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:27:02.000Z","msg":"央視表示，歐洲中心站記者孔琳琳已經獲釋，要求英國方面切實採取措施，保障央視記者權益。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，一名女子在英國保守黨年會一個有關香港議題的座談會上，批評發言者意圖分裂中國，又掌摑要求她離場的人，其後被警方拘捕。有報道指該名女子是央視記者，被掌摑的保守黨工作人員。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐倫敦大使館說，有中國記者在活動上提問表達觀點，但遭到百般阻撓及人身侵犯，完全不能接受，要求保守黨人權委員會停止干涉中國內政及插手香港事務，並要求會議組織者向中國記者道歉。大使館又說，英國保守黨利用該黨年會的周邊座談會，為反華分裂勢力張目，中方表示嚴重關切及強烈不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1420882-20181002.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1420882-20181002.htm&d=lejSInp4vmoBWxV5B205Sr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=967072f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1420882-20181002.htm&h=e23d3171\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1420882-20181002.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a11bb9afeff4c26750ae476ce988d6ccff3b95","tid":844395,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:31:29.000Z","msg":"英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中華大不列顛及北愛爾蘭聯合人民</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df98cb848825072989d32da27c0859ca14f827c","tid":844395,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.